    <li>✅ <strong>8 months</strong> of real-world hanging tests across 4 outdoor spaces</li>
    <li>✅ <strong>15 different products</strong> tested, from $18 to $120</li>
    <li>✅ <strong>Zero sponsored products</strong> — all purchased at retail</li>
